title: 211: Fitness Success Secrets for 2016
description: 2015 is winding down and 2016 will be the year that millions resolve to "get into shape" and then fail. Sal, Adam & Justin break down what it takes to successfully achieve your fitness goals in this coming year. Please subscribe, rate and review this show! Learn more about Mind Pump at www.mindpumpradio.com
